íŸ@bc45afe09103b94f724103f8f1afbfdbf63d970bc451eb2ee8c1cb083a2b931c⁄HTitle: title: ansi gradient
Path: Flags
Content:
``--fgstart, -a {string}``
: Foreground gradient start color in hex (0x123456).
``--fgend, -b {string}``
: Foreground gradient end color in hex.
``--bgstart, -c {string}``
: Background gradient start color in hex.
``--bgend, -d {string}``
: Background gradient end color in hex.
